@startuml
' ===============================
'   Project Architecture Diagram
'   Dark Theme (Safe + Compatible)
' ===============================

' Diagram layout
top to bottom direction

' General visual settings
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam roundcorner 15
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam ArrowColor #E0E7FF
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam backgroundColor #0F172A  ' dark navy background

' Activity element styling (safe syntax)
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #1E293B
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #60A5FA
skinparam ActivityFontColor #E2E8F0
skinparam ActivityFontName Arial
skinparam ActivityFontSize 12

' Start and end node colors (use safe skinparam keys)
skinparam StartColor #2563EB
skinparam EndColor #F43F5E

' Title (optional)
title **Medical Insurance Prediction – Project Architecture (Dark Theme)**

' ----- Diagram Flow -----
start

:Collect Dataset;
note right
Collect raw data:
age, BMI, region,
smoker status, etc.
end note

:Import Data to Colab;
:Analyse Data;
:Processing on Data;
note right
Data cleaning, encoding,
and feature engineering
end note

:Apply Regression Techniques;
note right
Regression algorithms:
• XGBoost  
• Gradient Boosting  
• Random Forest  
• Linear Model
end note

fork
  :XGBoost;
fork again
  :Gradient Boosting;
fork again
  :Random Forest;
fork again
  :Linear Model;
end fork

:Training Model;
:Testing Model;

:Predict Insurance Cost;
note right
Final Output:  
Predicted medical insurance premium
end note

stop
@enduml
